{
  "stem": "2522.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, by that time, you are ready to go any place that you can.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I don't care it's-- whether Madagascar or Cuba, just let's get out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But you can't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the thing is, sort of, the trap keeps closing and closing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in retrospect, you could have gone out if you would have taken certain risks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By the time you're ready to take those risks, those risks have already been cut off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just heightened anxiety.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there was not very much to explain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In some respects, many of the contingencies that were-- that my parents were planning and my father was planning, in fact, were not disclosed to us, the children, in the fear that I would sort of disclose things or inadvertently blab it out.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, so actually, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there is very little in there that I could say except an increased apprehension and, and tension in the family, which is an impact on family life.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The, the only thing that I remember was, you know, we have this Persian rug.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's in the main house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't want to leave it there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we now want to give the Persian rug as a graft to somebody who can give us certain privileges.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So those kind of discussions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we have a Contax camera, which was a very fancy, 35-millimeter camera.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, you, you start shedding voluntarily certain assets because they are going to be taken away anyway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So now you might as well give them away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thing that really overwhelms me in my memory of the '40, '41, particularly '42 is the increased bureaucratization.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
